paper/index.qmd:248:#| fig-cap: "Median total QALYs across the evidence-stance range, 100,000 draws per point, seed 0. The stance interpolates each tier's credibility mean piecewise-linearly from a near-RCT-only floor (non-randomized tiers at mean 0.01; randomized tier at its drafted mean) through the drafted best-guess tiers (0.5) to near face value (all means 0.999). A scenario path, not a bound; tier concentrations are held fixed."
